content.name: Channel spend with highest impact contribution

content.name: Channel Impact Contribution

description.header: Hmm. Now I need to consider the impact consideration between portfolio & brand for TV: TV continues to give me good return for the portfolio if not directly for any particular brand – So for loyal revenue I need to retain it
